+<p><b>Buildings:</b> build a Barracks for swordsmen and spearmen. Advance ages at the Town Center to unlock the Archery Range, Stable, and Siege Workshop — and stronger troops.</p>
     <p><b>Camera:</b> W A S D / arrows / screen edge to pan, mouse wheel to zoom, Q and E to rotate, middle-drag to pan. Click the minimap to jump.</p>
     <p><b>Keys:</b> S stop (with units selected) · F2 select all soldiers · <b>.</b> cycle idle villagers · Esc cancel/deselect · H help · M sound.</p>
 <p><b>Rally:</b> select a building and right-click the ground to set where new units go — rally your Town Center onto a resource and fresh villagers start gathering it immediately.</p>
